Sure, I can help with that! To get your ads out of pending, you should ensure the following steps are completed:
1. **Review Ad Content**: Make sure your ad content complies with our advertising policies.
2. **Check Targeting Settings**: Ensure your targeting settings are correctly configured for your audience.
3. **Verify Payment Information**: Confirm that your payment information is up to date and valid.
4. **Submit for Review**: If everything looks good, submit your ad for review again.
If you need more detailed guidance, please refer to our [Reporting Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18088532505485-Reporting-Guide). If you still encounter issues, feel free to contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.

I understand how that can be confusing. Sometimes, additional information is required after an initial review to ensure compliance with our policies and to verify the legitimacy of your business. This can happen if there are updates to our verification process or if more details are needed for security reasons.
To resolve this, please provide the requested information as soon as possible. If you need further assistance, you can refer to our [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next) for more details or contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
what is the request information

The requested information typically includes details about your business such as:
1. **Business Name**: The official name of your business.
2. **Business Address**: The physical address where your business operates.
3. **Tax Identification Number (TIN)**: Your business's tax ID for verification purposes.
4. **Contact Information**: A valid phone number and email address for your business.
5. **Proof of Business Registration**: Documents that prove your business is legally registered, such as a certificate of incorporation or a business license.
6. **Description of Services/Products**: A brief description of the services or products your business offers.
If you have any specific questions about the information needed, please refer to our [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next) or contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
